List the sector taxonomy (id + display name in the requested language). Default: `lang` follows the caller's language; `includeInvisible=false` returns ~1,091 visible sectors.

{{include:headers/tool-when-to-use}} to resolve a free-text sector name (e.g. "Healthcare") into the sector ids that leadbay_adjust_audience needs.

{{include:headers/tool-when-not-to-use}} when you already have sector ids — pass them directly.
